<\/p><p>In April 2025, Worthy Products entered a new chapter when Worthy acquired the company in the North Island, expanding their FMCG portfolio and bringing fresh resources, leadership, and a renewed vision to grow. Today, as part of the Worthy group, Worthy Products continues to deliver leading brands to retailers and customers across New Zealand, with an unwavering commitment to quality, service, and innovation.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","text_size":"t2"}}},"block_order":["heading_RNbzRz","text_bgUFdD"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Introduction_About_us_Page.png","desktop_section_height":500,"mobile_section_height":400,"desktop_media_width":47,"desktop_media_scale":100,"layout":"media_first","image_cover":true,"desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","text_max_width":"m","content_layout":"overlap","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"scheme-2","show_content_shadow":true,"line_separator":"","top_padding":"pt-s15","bottom_padding":"pb-s","visibility":"","hide_when_empty":false,"show_at_specific_time_of_day":false,"show_time_morning":true,"show_time_afternoon":true,"show_time_evening":true,"show_time_night":true}},"image_with_text_jHi6y4":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_h9h9fG":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Growing","heading_italic_convert":"","heading_size":"h2","heading_size_custom":2.4,"heading_line_height_custom":1.2,"heading_tag":"h2"}},"text_gJzhhW":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Under Worthy’s leadership, Worthy Products has entered an exciting new phase of growth and transformation. With the backing and resources of a leading FMCG group, we have expanded our distribution network, strengthened relationships with global suppliers, and introduced a broader range of products to the New Zealand market. <\/p><p>Worthy’s ownership has brought a renewed focus on innovation, operational excellence, and customer service, empowering our team to deliver greater value and reliability to retailers and customers across the country.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","text_size":"t2"}},"icon_hkJtAH":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"rocket","icon_container":"rounded","icon_size":3.4,"icon_color":"#ffffff","icon_background_color":"#ededed","background_gradient":"linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(216, 57, 132, 1), rgba(158, 15, 189, 1) 100%)"}}},"block_order":["heading_h9h9fG","text_gJzhhW","icon_hkJtAH"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/V_J_TRADING_EXTERIOR.png","desktop_section_height":400,"mobile_section_height":400,"desktop_media_width":55,"desktop_media_scale":100,"layout":"text_first","image_cover":true,"desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","text_max_width":"m","content_layout":"overlap","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"scheme-2","show_content_shadow":true,"line_separator":"","top_padding":"pt-0","bottom_padding":"pb-s","visibility":"","hide_when_empty":false,"show_at_specific_time_of_day":false,"show_time_morning":true,"show_time_afternoon":true,"show_time_evening":true,"show_time_night":true}},"image_with_text_tqGFGy":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_YRrr4G":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Future","heading_italic_convert":"","heading_size":"h2","heading_size_custom":2.4,"heading_line_height_custom":1.2,"heading_tag":"h2"}},"text_ebWYHa":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><br\/>Looking ahead, Worthy Products is excited about what the future holds. With Worthy behind us, we’re not just growing our range of snacks and drinks. We’re also investing in smarter ways to deliver them to stores and customers across New Zealand. <\/p><p>Our team is always looking for new ways to make things simpler, faster, and better for the people we work with every day. We want every retailer to feel confident that with Worthy Products, they’ll always have access to the world’s best brands, backed by service they can trust. The journey is just getting started, and we can’t wait to see where it takes us next.<br\/><br\/><\/p>"